# Intuition
Thumb-Rule: If need to detect a cycle anywhere first use Fast-Slow Pointer method.

# Approach
Use the Two pointer Approach. Fast pointer will move ahead by two nodes and slow pointer willl move one node. If they meet at certain point, then it confirms the availability of the cycle.

# Complexity
- Time complexity: O(n)


- Space complexity: O(1)


